dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Lease Areas for Oregon released in 2024. They were developed based on extensive outreach and suitability modeling. The suitability modeling process was a joint effort between BOEM and the National Centers for Coastal Ocean Sciences (NCCOS). The report (A Wind Energy Area Siting Analysis for the Oregon Call Area) describing the methods is available on the BOEM website: https://www.boem.gov/renewable-energy/state-activities/Oregon

The services, information, and data made available herein are provided 'as is' without warranties of any kind. Not for navigational use.
